<title>DeepSeek发布DSpark推测解码框架，将DeepSeek-V4单用户生成速度较MTP-1提升60–85%</title>
<link>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/27/deepseek-releases-dspark-a-speculative-decoding-framework-that-accelerates-deepseek-v4-per-user-generation-60-85-over-mtp-1/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.marktechpost.com/?p=80747</guid>
<pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 16:59:58 +0000</pubDate>
<source>marktechpost.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【marktechpost.com】DeepSeek开源了DSpark，这是一个推测解码框架，可为现有DeepSeek-V4权重附加草稿模块。该框架将并行草稿主干与轻量级马尔可夫头配对以削减后缀衰减，并引入基于置信度的验证机制，根据实时GPU负载动态调整待校验令牌数量。离线测试中，其接受长度较DFlash和Eagle3提升16–31%；生产环境下，单用户生成速度较MTP-1基线无损提升57–85%。训练代码库DeepSpec采用MIT许可证发布。<br/><br/><a href="https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/27/deepseek-releases-dspark-a-speculative-decoding-framework-that-accelerates-deepseek-v4-per-user-generation-60-85-over-mtp-1/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
</item>
